T1  - ESTIMATION OF DYNAMIC DISCRETE CHOICE MODELS BY MAXIMUM LIKELIHOOD AND THE SIMULATED METHOD OF MOMENTS
AU  - Eisenhauer, Philipp
AU  - Heckman, James J.
AU  - Mosso, Stefano
Y1  - 2015/05/01
PY  - 2015
DA  - 2015/05/01
